* Compute & Development\nNaming Conventions
** Clusters
***_ {environment}_{domain}_cluster
***_ dev_sales_cluster, prod_etl_cluster
** Jobs
***_ job_{layer}_{purpose}
***_ job_bronze_orders_ingestion
** Pipelines
***_ pipe_{domain}
***_ stream_{source}_to_{target}
** Notebooks
***_ notebook_{layer}_{purpose}
***_ Organized by bronze/silver/gold folders
** Repositories
***_ repo_{project_name}
** Dashboards
***_ dashboard_{domain}_{purpose}
@endmindmap
